bd-freecad-library
==================

This project contains parametric build123d Python implementations of parts
that are described in the FreeCAD Parts Library:

    https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD-library
    License: LGPL-2.1-or-later

The dimensional data tables in this project (in DIMENSIONS.md files under
docs/standards/...) are drawn from international standards (ISO / DIN /
ANSI / EN), with the FreeCAD Parts Library as the cross-reference source
for variant geometry.

The Python implementations themselves are independent rewrites, not
verbatim translations. They are licensed under MIT (see LICENSE).

When using this library, attribute the FreeCAD Parts Library if your
distribution includes any dimension tables that originate from there.
